**Usage:** Environments will appear in **database object names** (databases, warehouses, roles).
{%- elif account_strategy == "Multi-Account (Environment-based)" %}
**Usage:** Environments will appear in **account names**.
{%- elif account_strategy == "Multi-Account (Domain-based)" %}
